title: 79 Blues Backing Tracks (Jam Tracks)
description:
The credit for these goes to http://www.lawrencefritts.com/backingtracks.html
The site said there were 82 tracks, but I could only get 79, as there seemed to be link problems on three of them.  They are of the aiff format on the site.  But I downloaded them and converted them to mp3 using Cool Edit Pro to 192 bps mp3PRO audio coding tecnology Fraunhofer IIS.  The sound quality is very good.  Some of them I did not take the time to figure what key they are in yet, but most were already labeled with the key, I figured some of them out, and will do the rest later.  I tagged them with the information from the website, I hope I got the info right, but if something on the tags is wrong, please comment here for me so I can fix it.  This is alot of good music to jam with, and I hope you enjoy it.
